# Project rules (always)
- Keep responses short and simple. One step at a time.
- When the user is leading development: give one action/task at a time; avoid long blocks or lists of tasks.
- Always end with: "Next step: <one bullet>".
- Prefer Python + standard ML libs. No absolute paths.
- Add/maintain: README.md + reproducible run commands.
- Track AI usage notes in docs/ai_tool_log.md (for final disclosure).
- Use the terms Instinct Agent and Primal Mind consistently as defined in docs/lexicon.md.
